  "notes": "WAT: Confirma reservas. Inputs: reservation_id, user_name, user_email, phone, company, industry, agent_name/slug, plan_interest, preferred_date. Outputs: email HTML al lead, alerta HTML al admin, fila en Reservations Pipeline, evento en Google Calendar (si hay fecha). continueOnFail en Gmail/Sheets para resiliencia."
